data.description: This rare 3 bedroom corner Villa with beautifully renovated kitchen and baths in 55+ plus 700 credit score required. The spacious main living area has a vaulted ceiling and largeskylight. Stunning high end kitchen with granite counter tops, European style cabinetry and breakfast area with slider to outside sitting space. Bathrooms with granite counters, newer cabinets and toilets. Shower in master with seat and tub in second bath with frameless shower door. Neutral tile flooring throughout main living area, kitchen and hallway. Laminate floors in bedrooms. Tons of closet space including large walk-in in master. Full size washer/dryer conveniently located between all bedrooms. The patio is enclosed and air conditioned which gives an additional room if desired or use as an open patio Bonus storage there as well. A/C & Water Heater 2019.This 55 plus gated community includes a wonderful clubhouse which is currently being renovated. Must see to appreciate.
